Resource Profile: FR Core Practitioner Profile

Official URL: http://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/StructureDefinition/fr-core-practitioner Version: 2.0.0
Active as of 2023-09-19 Computable Name: FRCorePractitionerProfile

French profile of the Practitioner resource Profil de la ressource Practitionner pour la France
This profile specifies the types of identifiers for practitioners in France Ce profil contraint les types d’identifiants du professionnel de santé en France

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: FR Core Appointment Operator Extension, FR Core Appointment Profile, FR Core Encounter Profile, FR Core Medication Administration Inhaled Oxygen Profile... Show 13 more, FR Core Observation Bmi Profile, FR Core Observation Body Height Profile, FR Core Observation Body Temperature Profile, FR Core Observation Body Weight Profile, FR Core Observation Bp Profile, FR Core Observation Head Circum Profile, FR Core Observation Heart Rate Profile, FR Core Oservation Resp Rate Profile, FR Core Observation Oxygen Saturation Profile, FR Core Patient Profile, FR Core Practitioner Role Exercice, FR Core Practitioner Role Profession and FR Core Schedule Profile
